xt sequence of actions for this turn, in order, and finish with DONE."'}, {'role': 'user', 'content': '{"stimuli": [{"type": "CONVERSATION", "content": "Network telemetry observations: InitialAccess on svc-web from red", "source": ""}]}'}]
